<h1>边</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#990000;">biān</span><span class=alesi>(bian1)</span> , bian <span class=lesi>// pronunciations of 边 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 边</h2><div class=abo>
<p><b>Unihan definition:</b> <a href="/dictionary/edge" style="color:black;">edge</a>, <a href="/dictionary/margin" style="color:black;">margin</a>, <a href="/dictionary/side" style="color:black;">side</a>, border</p><p><b>Number of strokes:</b> 5<br><small>Examples of other characters consisting of 5 strokes: <a href="/character/他" title="ta1: other, another; he, she, it">他</a>, <a href="/character/们" title="men: adjunct pronoun indicate plural">们</a>, <a href="/character/出" title="chu1: go out, send out; stand; produce">出</a>, <a href="/character/可" title="ke3: may, can, -able; possibly">可</a>, <a href="/character/对" title="dui4: correct, right; facing, opposed">对</a>, <a href="/character/生" title="sheng1: life, living, lifetime; birth">生</a>, <a href="/character/发" title="fa1: issue, dispatch, send out; hair">发</a>, <a href="/character/用" title="yong4: use, employ, apply, operate; use">用</a>, <a href="/character/去" title="qu4: go away, leave, depart">去</a>, <a href="/character/主" title="zhu3: master, chief owner; host; lord">主</a></small></p><p><b>Radical:</b> <a href="/character/辵" title="Kangxi radical 162">辵</a>&nbsp;162.2</p><p><b>HSK level:</b> 2 <br><small>Other HSK 2 characters: <a href="/character/告" title="gao4: tell, announce, inform; accuse">告</a>, <a href="/character/望" title="wang4: to look at, look forward; to hope, expect">望</a>, <a href="/character/路" title="lu4: road, path, street; journey">路</a>, <a href="/character/色" title="se4: color, tint, hue, shade; form, body; beauty, desire for beauty">色</a>, <a href="/character/共" title="gong4: together with, all, total; to share">共</a>, <a href="/character/完" title="wan2: complete, finish, settle; whole">完</a>, <a href="/character/思" title="si1: think, consider, ponder; final particle">思</a>, <a href="/character/让" title="rang4: allow, permit, yield, concede">让</a>, <a href="/character/运" title="yun4: run; simplified form of 運 luck, fortune; ship, transport">运</a>, <a href="/character/白" title="bai2: w